<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.3.8">
<l>eṉkuṟṟa mēyeṉṟu collavum vēṇṭākā</l>
<l rend="indent">ṇeṉṉaināṉ maṇṇuṇṭē ṉāka</l>
<l>vaṉpuṟṟu nōkki yaṭittum piṭittu</l>
<l rend="indent">maṉaivarkkuṅ kāṭṭiṟ ṟilaiyē</l>
<l>vaṉpuṟ ṟaraviṉ pakaikkoṭi vāmaṉa</l>
<l rend="indent">nampiyuṉ kātukaḷ tūrum</l>
<l>tuṉpuṟ ṟaṉavellān tīrppāy pirāṉē</l>
<l rend="indent">tiriyiṭṭuc collukēṉ meyyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Look, don’t say ‘It is my fault’!</l>
<l>While I consumed the earth,</l>
<l>looking at me with [such] love,</l>
<l>you caught and beat me,</l>
<l>as everyone looked on, no?</l>
<l>Vamana Nampi, whose banner is the enemy</l>
<l>of the serpent in the strong anthill,</l>
<l rend="indent">your ears [will] close up.</l>
<l>Lord who is the cure for all suffering,</l>
<l>[let me] place the thread, I speak the truth!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
